587
00:29:44,519 --> 00:29:46,848
(Memorandum, So Geum Ja)

588
00:29:46,848 --> 00:29:49,888
I, So Geum Ja,
promise to uphold the following...

589
00:29:49,888 --> 00:29:52,658
in exchange for receiving
the 30,000 dollars...

590
00:29:52,858 --> 00:29:55,759
Baek Mi Ja once received
from Kim Jun Sub 15 years ago...

591
00:29:55,999 --> 00:29:59,398
plus an interest of 20,000 dollars.

592
00:30:00,329 --> 00:30:01,339
One.

593
00:30:01,698 --> 00:30:05,809
I will never appear before
Baek Mi Ja and Park Do Ra again.

594
00:30:06,908 --> 00:30:10,608
I will never speak of the incident
involving Baek Mi Ja.

595
00:30:10,608 --> 00:30:12,648
If I do not uphold the following,

596
00:30:12,878 --> 00:30:15,918
I will pay back
triple the amount of 50,000 dollars.

597
00:30:17,049 --> 00:30:18,049
Also,

598
00:30:18,789 --> 00:30:20,249
I will compensate...

599
00:30:20,688 --> 00:30:23,458
for any damages
suffered by Park Do Ra...

600
00:30:23,888 --> 00:30:25,259
because of the words I spill.

601
00:30:27,190 --> 00:30:30,930
(Pureun Bank)

602
00:30:36,601 --> 00:30:38,270
