- Sit down.

608
00:31:02,391 --> 00:31:03,420
Hyun Chul.

609
00:31:03,420 --> 00:31:04,430
You...

610
00:31:05,091 --> 00:31:06,490
Don't be startled.

611
00:31:06,490 --> 00:31:08,160
