out of your father-in-law...

620
00:31:32,750 --> 00:31:34,291
plus 20,000 dollars in interest.

621
00:31:34,291 --> 00:31:37,930
In total, I received
50,000 dollars from her.

622
00:31:38,990 --> 00:31:40,960
What the...

623
00:31:40,960 --> 00:31:43,101
Did she easily give up the money?

624
00:31:43,101 --> 00:31:44,930
Come on.

625
00:31:44,930 --> 00:31:47,331
She tried to talk her way out of it,

626
00:31:47,331 --> 00:31:48,871
but I said I'd go
to the broadcasting station...

627
00:31:48,871 --> 00:31:50,541
and tell people
that Do Ra owed us money...

628
00:31:50,541 --> 00:31:52,240
in hopes of tanking her career.

629
00:31:52,871 --> 00:31:54,710
She caved into my threats.

630
00:31:55,081 --> 00:31:56,541
Mom, please.

631
00:31:56,541 --> 00:31:57,881
What's so wrong about it?

632
00:31:57,881 --> 00:32:00,851
I got the job done,
so who cares how I got it?

633
00:32:00,851 --> 00:32:02,750
Mom, come on.

634
00:32:03,520 --> 00:32:06,520
Why did you bring it home in cash
when this can be dangerous?

635
00:32:06,520 --> 00:32:08,190
If I wire you the money,

636
00:32:08,190 --> 00:32:09,861
your wife might find out.

637
00:32:10,291 --> 00:32:13,160
Also, money like this
should be spent in cash.

638
00:32:13,690 --> 00:32:15,730
Depositing it in a bank...

639
00:32:15,730 --> 00:32:17,061
will lead to it being traced.

640
00:32:17,700 --> 00:32:18,730
I guess.

641
00:32:19,930 --> 00:32:20,970
Hyun Chul.

642
00:32:21,601 --> 00:32:24,841
I'm telling you to use this money...

643
00:32:24,841 --> 00:32:26,670
to get settled down.

644
00:32:26,670 --> 00:32:28,980
Start a lucrative business.

645
00:32:29,581 --> 00:32:33,510
That way, you'll be able
to be a proud husband.

646
00:32:34,010 --> 00:32:35,220
Mom...

647
00:32:36,220 --> 00:32:38,690
Don't make any mistakes this time...

648
00:32:38,690 --> 00:32:42,160
and test every bridge
before crossing it.

649
00:32:42,361 --> 00:32:43,791
Got it, Mom.

650
00:32:44,831 --> 00:32:46,291
But this...

651
00:32:46,291 --> 00:32:49,031
Sun Young will throw a fit
when she finds out about it.

652
00:32:49,031 --> 00:32:52,470
How will she know
if we don't tell her?

653
00:32:52,470 --> 00:32:55,970
We will take this to our graves.

654
00:32:56,440 --> 00:32:58,270
- It's our secret.
- I'm home.

655
00:32:58,841 --> 00:33:00,141
What...

656
00:33:00,141 --> 00:33:01,581
- Is no one home?
- What?

657
00:33:02,381 --> 00:33:03,841
- Hey.
- Honey?

658
00:33:05,051 --> 00:33:06,051
- What?
- Gosh.

659
00:33:06,851 --> 00:33:08,781
But his shoes are by the door.

660
00:33:09,020 --> 00:33:10,281
What's going on?

661
00:33:10,450 --> 00:33:11,450
Honey?

662
00:33:12,151 --> 00:33:13,151
Mother?

663
00:33:17,020 --> 00:33:19,190
- What...
- Why is this door locked?

664
00:33:19,460 --> 00:33:22,230
Honey? Mother?
Honey, are you in here?

665
00:33:22,361 --> 00:33:24,331
- Yes. What is it?
- What's up?

666
00:33:24,331 --> 00:33:26,571
Why is this door locked?

667
00:33:26,571 --> 00:33:29,770
What? Is the door locked?

668
00:33:29,770 --> 00:33:31,270
Yes, Mother.

669
00:33:32,470 --> 00:33:33,710
Open it.

670
00:33:34,740 --> 00:33:36,410
- Here.
- Hey.

671
00:33:36,581 --> 00:33:37,611
Mom.

672
00:33:38,710 --> 00:33:40,480
- What is it?
- Well...

673
00:33:40,851 --> 00:33:43,081
Honey, you're home.

674
00:33:43,480 --> 00:33:44,490
