00:35:46,040 --> 00:35:47,210
Oh, no.

706
00:35:47,210 --> 00:35:49,781
I'm sorry. I forgot my lines.

707
00:35:50,040 --> 00:35:52,250
Bong Soo, I'm sorry.
Are you all right?

708
00:35:52,250 --> 00:35:53,250
Cut. No good.

709
00:35:53,651 --> 00:35:54,681
I'm fine.

710
00:35:54,681 --> 00:35:56,951
I'm really sorry.

711
00:35:57,051 --> 00:35:58,520
Bong Soo, I'm sorry.

712
00:35:58,520 --> 00:35:59,750
It can happen.

713
00:35:59,750 --> 00:36:00,821
- Yoon Jung!
- Gosh.

714
00:36:01,361 --> 00:36:03,661
Let's get the scene done this time.

715
00:36:04,161 --> 00:36:05,361
Please get ready.

716
00:36:05,361 --> 00:36:06,631
Sure.

717
00:36:08,261 --> 00:36:09,330
Ready.

718
00:36:09,931 --> 00:36:12,301
One, two, ready. Action.

719
00:36:13,301 --> 00:36:15,201
How could you do this to me?

720
00:36:16,640 --> 00:36:19,210
You punk. Yesterday, you...

721
00:36:20,670 --> 00:36:22,140
Cut. No good.

722
00:36:22,741 --> 00:36:23,841
What the...

723
00:36:24,911 --> 00:36:26,051
Snark Do Ra.

724
00:36:26,451 --> 00:36:29,651
That hurt more than
getting hit with a fly swatter!

725
00:36:29,651 --> 00:36:31,690
I was trying to make it work
in one go.

726
00:36:31,690 --> 00:36:33,350
Gosh. Bong Soo, does it hurt badly?

727
00:36:33,350 --> 00:36:34,591
I'm fine.

728
00:36:34,591 --> 00:36:36,960
It only happened because
she was immersed in her character,

729
00:36:36,960 --> 00:36:39,031
- so please be understanding.
- Sure.

730
00:36:39,031 --> 00:36:40,491
I'm sorry.

731
00:36:41,091 --> 00:36:42,761
Are you all right?

732
00:36:42,761 --> 00:36:43,761
- Yes.
- Is everything good?

733
00:36:43,761 --> 00:36:45,431
Yes, just a second.

734
00:36:46,071 --> 00:36:48,040
- Are you all right?
- Yes.

735
00:36:48,040 --> 00:36:50,870
One, two, ready. Action.

736
00:36:51,370 --> 00:36:53,210
How could you do this to me?

737
00:36:55,080 --> 00:36:56,310
You punk.

738
00:36:56,640 --> 00:36:57,850
My nose.

739
00:36:57,850 --> 00:36:59,810
Cut. No good!

740
00:37:00,210 --> 00:37:01,321
Snark Do Ra.

741
00:37:01,721 --> 00:37:03,951
You did that on purpose
to mess with me.

742
00:37:03,951 --> 00:37:05,850
- Get over here.
- Not this again.

743
00:37:05,850 --> 00:37:07,520
Bong Soo, you're wrong.

744
00:37:07,520 --> 00:37:10,120
Mr. Cha, that wasn't it.
She said so herself.

745
00:37:10,120 --> 00:37:11,661
- Please let it go.
- As if.

746
00:37:11,661 --> 00:37:14,161
That cow did it on purpose!

747
00:37:14,161 --> 00:37:16,531
- Ms. Park...
- Did you just call me a cow?

748
00:37:16,531 --> 00:37:19,201
