not to add scenes...

753
00:37:30,540 --> 00:37:32,051
that involve throwing water,

754
00:37:32,051 --> 00:37:33,310
so please calm down.

755
00:37:33,810 --> 00:37:35,120
On American TV shows,

756
00:37:35,721 --> 00:37:38,051
they shoot people
rather than throw water.

757
00:37:38,321 --> 00:37:39,350
Bang.

758
00:37:43,390 --> 00:37:45,261
I can't work with Bong Soo.

759
00:37:45,790 --> 00:37:46,991
I didn't do it on purpose.

760
00:37:46,991 --> 00:37:48,230
